Title: iPad 3 Diagnostic Service
Body (HTML):
iPad 3 Diagnostic Service

 

At iFixYouri, we understand. Your iPad 3 is really important to you. When it breaks, it can really mess up your day. If you are in need of Diagnostic Service, let the professional repair technicians at iFixYouri help you out.

 

*NOTE: If you decline repairs for diagnostic or water damage treatment or your device is deemed non-repairable, you will be responsible for shipping and handling.

This is the service you need if you aren't quite sure what the problem with your iPad 3 is. We'll find out what is going on, and contact you with a repair quote.

 

Every repair service begins with a series of diagnostic tests to determine what the issue is. Our technicians use their repair experience to quickly diagnose the problem. In most cases, repairs are minimal; however, if we see that your iPad 3 has additional damage, we'll contact you before proceeding.

 

Send your iPad 3 to iFixYouri via the UPS shipping method of your choosing. Please ship your device in a sturdy, secure box. If you hear it rattling around in the box, add some more padding. Please do not include cases, cables, or accessories. Standard UPS Ground is covered by us, as well as $100 insurance. Faster shipping and extra insurance coverage can be purchased using the drop-down boxes above.

 

Questions about Diagnostic Service? Type them into the box below, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible. Alternatively, you can reach us at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com

Title: iPad 3 Glass Repair
Body (HTML):
iPad 3 Glass Repair

 

The iPad 3 has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Glass Repair.

 

Each device has its own lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years if properly maintained. Drops, water or liquid, even a jolt can damage your device.

Those who have both cracked glass and a broken LCD should opt for our iPad 3 Glass & LCD Repair. This service is for glass breakage only.

 

With Glass Repair for iPad 3, iFixYouri is here to help. With this service, our repair technicians inspect the problem, as well as any other affected components, repair your device, and send it back to you asap. If there are any other issues affecting your device, we'll let you know and proceed with those repairs only after your approval.

 

We email you a printable shipping label, and include $100 of insurance protection. If you would like faster shipping or more insurance coverage, you have the option to upgrade above using the drop-downs.

 

All replacement parts come with a 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage.

 

Do you have any questions about Glass Repair from iFixYouri? Just ask them in the box below, and we'll get back to you. Alternatively, you can always reach us via our support phone number 888-494-4349 or email support@ifixyouri.com

iPad 3 Ear Speaker Repair

 

We recommend not trying Ear Speaker Repair yourself. Devices have become more and more sophisticated and you may cause more damage. Using the supplied shipping label, send your iPad 3 to iFixYouri's mail-in center so our skilled repair technicians can inspect your device, pinpoint all/any issues affecting it, and get them repaired the professional way.

 

After checkout, you'll receive an email confirmation and shipping label. When your phone arrives at our repair center, we do diagnostic tests to determine if any other issues are at play. Outgoing testing ensures that your iPad 3 is fully functional. With the repairs complete, we send you a tracking number and ship your iPad 3 back to you!

 

We email you a printable shipping label, and include $100 of insurance protection. If you would like faster shipping or more insurance coverage, you have the option to upgrade above using the drop-downs.

 

A 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage is included. Contact customer service with any questions at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com.

Title: iPad 3 Vibrate Switch Repair
Body (HTML):
iPad 3 Vibrate Switch Repair

 

The iPad 3 has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Vibrate Switch Repair.

 

Each device has its own lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years if properly maintained. Drops, water or liquid, even a jolt can damage your device.

 

iFixYouri is here to solve your problem with Vibrate Switch Repair for iPad 3. With this service, we'll determine the extent of the damage, get your device repaired, and send it back to you. We'll let you know if there are any other issues affecting your device and give you the option of proceeding with those repairs.

 

Faster shipping options and extra insurance protection are available for purchase if you'd like. Simply choose from the drop-downs before adding to your shopping cart. When packaging your device, use a sturdy, secure box. You do not need to ship us your cases, cables, or accessories.

 

A 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage comes with every repair.

 

Do you have any questions about Vibrate Switch Repair from iFixYouri? Just ask them in the box below, and we'll get back to you. Alternatively, you can always reach us via our support phone number 888-494-4349 or email support@ifixyouri.com
